# Team Portfolio Website

A modern, responsive portfolio website built with Next.js 15, featuring a sleek glassmorphism design and comprehensive team showcase capabilities.

## 🌟 Overview

This is a professional team portfolio website that showcases our development team's skills, projects, and services. The site features a modern dark theme with glassmorphism effects, smooth animations, and a fully responsive design optimized for all devices.

## 🚀 Website Content Summary

### Main Sections

- **Homepage**: Hero section with animated tech stack badges, featured projects showcase, team capabilities overview, and contact CTA
- **About**: Comprehensive team information, company values, tech stack showcase, and mission statement
- **Projects**: Complete portfolio of team projects with filtering, detailed project cards, and individual project pages
- **Services**: Full service offerings including web development, mobile apps, UI/UX design, and SEO optimization
- **Offers**: Pricing plans (Basic $99, Professional $499, Enterprise Custom) and service packages
- **Blog**: Technical articles and insights from the team
- **Contact**: Multiple contact methods and inquiry forms

### Key Features Showcased

- **Modern Development**: Cutting-edge technologies and best practices
- **Lightning Fast**: Optimized performance and fast load times
- **Team Collaboration**: Experienced team working together
- **Rapid Deployment**: Efficient CI/CD processes
- **Frontend Development**: React, Next.js, modern CSS frameworks
- **Backend Development**: Robust APIs, databases, server solutions
- **UI/UX Design**: Beautiful, intuitive user experiences
- **Mobile Development**: Cross-platform mobile applications
- **SEO Optimization**: Search engine optimization services
- **Performance Optimization**: Speed and user experience focus

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

### Frontend
- **Next.js 15** - React framework with App Router
- **React 18** - UI library
- **TypeScript** - Type safety
- **Tailwind CSS** - Utility-first CSS framework
- **Shadcn/ui** - Modern component library
- **Lucide React** - Icon library

### Styling & Design
- **Glassmorphism Effects** - Modern glass-like UI elements
- **CSS Custom Properties** - Dynamic theming system
- **Responsive Design** - Mobile-first approach
- **Dark Theme** - Professional dark color scheme
- **Gradient Animations** - Smooth visual effects

### Database & Backend
- **Neon Database** - PostgreSQL serverless database
- **Server Actions** - Next.js server-side functionality
- **SQL** - Database queries and operations

### Development Tools
- **ESLint** - Code linting
- **PostCSS** - CSS processing
- **PNPM** - Package manager
- **Git** - Version control

## 📁 Project Structure

```
team-portfolio/
├── app/                    # Next.js App Router
│   ├── about/             # About page
│   ├── api/               # API routes
│   ├── blog/              # Blog pages
│   ├── contact/           # Contact page
│   ├── offers/            # Pricing and offers
│   ├── projects/          # Projects showcase
│   ├── services/          # Services overview
│   ├── globals.css        # Global styles
│   ├── layout.tsx         # Root layout
│   └── page.tsx           # Homepage
├── components/            # Reusable components
│   ├── ui/                # Shadcn/ui components
│   ├── project-card.tsx   # Project display component
│   ├── tech-badge.tsx     # Technology badges
│   └── ...                # Other components
├── hooks/                 # Custom React hooks
├── lib/                   # Utility functions
│   ├── db.ts              # Database configuration
│   ├── theme-config.ts    # Theme configuration
│   └── utils.ts           # General utilities
├── public/                # Static assets
├── styles/                # Additional stylesheets
└── ...                    # Configuration files
```

## 🎨 Design System

### Color Palette
- **Primary**: Cyan blue (#00BFFF)
- **Accent**: Bright cyan (#00CED1)
- **Background**: Dark gradient (hsl(220, 30%, 5%) to hsl(220, 25%, 8%))
- **Text**: High contrast white/muted combinations
- **Glass Cards**: Semi-transparent with backdrop blur

### Typography
- **Orbitron**: Display font for headings and gradients
- **System fonts**: Clean, readable body text
- **Font weights**: 500, 700 for emphasis

### Components
- **Glass Cards**: Backdrop blur with subtle borders
- **Glow Effects**: Hover animations with color transitions
- **Tech Badges**: Pill-shaped technology indicators
- **Gradient Text**: Animated color transitions
- **Responsive Grid**: Flexible layouts for all screen sizes

## 🚀 Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- Node.js 18+ 
- PNPM (recommended) or npm
- Git

### Installation

1. **Clone the repository**
   ```bash
   git clone <repository-url>
   cd team-portfolio
   ```

2. **Install dependencies**
   ```bash
   pnpm install
   # or
   npm install
   ```

3. **Set up environment variables**
   ```bash
   cp .env.local.example .env.local
   ```
   
   Add your database and other configuration variables:
   ```
   DATABASE_URL=your_neon_database_url
   NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=http://localhost:3000
   ```

4. **Run the development server**
   ```bash
   pnpm dev
   # or
   npm run dev
   ```

5. **Open your browser**
   Navigate to [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000)

## 📜 Available Scripts

```bash
# Development
pnpm dev          # Start development server
pnpm build        # Build for production
pnpm start        # Start production server
pnpm lint         # Run ESLint

# Package management
pnpm install      # Install dependencies
pnpm add <pkg>    # Add new package
```

## 🗄️ Database Schema

The application uses Neon PostgreSQL with the following main tables:

- **projects**: Portfolio projects with metadata
- **team_members**: Team member information and profiles
- **blog_posts**: Blog articles and content
- **inquiries**: Contact form submissions

## 🎯 Key Features

### Performance Optimizations
- **Next.js App Router**: Latest routing system
- **Image Optimization**: Automatic WebP conversion
- **Code Splitting**: Automatic bundle optimization
- **Static Generation**: Pre-rendered pages where possible
- **Font Optimization**: Self-hosted Google Fonts

### Responsive Design
- **Mobile-first**: Optimized for mobile devices
- **Breakpoints**: Tailored for all screen sizes
- **Touch-friendly**: Large tap targets and gestures
- **Fast loading**: Optimized images and assets

### Accessibility
- **Semantic HTML**: Proper heading structure
- **ARIA labels**: Screen reader support
- **Keyboard navigation**: Full keyboard accessibility
- **Color contrast**: WCAG compliant contrast ratios

### SEO Optimization
- **Meta tags**: Dynamic OpenGraph and Twitter cards
- **Structured data**: JSON-LD schema markup
- **Sitemap**: Automatic sitemap generation
- **Performance**: Core Web Vitals optimization

## 🌐 Deployment

### Vercel (Recommended)
1. Push your code to GitHub
2. Connect your repository to Vercel
3. Add environment variables in Vercel dashboard
4. Deploy automatically on every push

### Manual Deployment
```bash
# Build the application
pnpm build

# Start production server
pnpm start
```

## 🔧 Configuration

### Theme Customization
Edit `lib/theme-config.ts` to customize colors, fonts, and other design tokens.

### Content Management
- Update project data in the database
- Modify static content in page components
- Add new team members through the admin interface

### Environment Variables
```bash
DATABASE_URL=                 # Neon PostgreSQL connection string
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=        # Your domain URL
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=           # Google Analytics ID (optional)
```

